de.unistuttgart.vis.wearable.os.storage

Class SensorDataSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unistuttgart.vis.wearable.os.storage.SensorDataSerializer

  • public class SensorDataSerializer
extends java.lang.Object
    Serialize sensor Data and save them to a file. Note that no duplicates will be saved. Duplicated data sets are recognized by their time stamp the data has been recorded on. This values will be skipped.

    roehrdor
